    <div class="project-overview">
        <h2 class="section-title">Project Overview</h2>
        <div class="overview-text">
            "Fishing with Dad" was an intimate, heartfelt campaign that explored how Meta technologies help preserve and share life's precious moments across generations. The story followed a father and son's fishing tradition, showing how sharing these experiences through Meta platforms creates lasting memories that can be revisited and cherished.
            <br><br>
            The campaign emphasized Meta's role in connecting families and preserving personal narratives in an increasingly digital world. Through authentic storytelling, we demonstrated how technology can enhance rather than replace meaningful human experiences. The work focused on emotional resonance over feature explanations, showing the human impact of staying connected.
            <br><br>
            The campaign performed exceptionally well in terms of emotional engagement metrics and brand sentiment, particularly among family-focused demographics. It reinforced Meta's positioning as a company that understands and facilitates the relationships that matter most, moving beyond utility to tap into deeper human truths about connection and legacy.
        </div>
    </div>

